---
description: Rules for safe refactoring
globs: "**/*.py"
alwaysApply: false
---

- Never rewrite `main_original.py` unless explicitly asked.
- Preserve current behavior before improving behavior.
- Prefer small diffs.
- Do not mix refactor changes with format-compatibility changes.
- Do not move acquisition/download orchestration out of the monolith unless explicitly asked.
- When behavior must change, call it out explicitly before implementing.